3. write a program in java to convert any image file(.jpg, .bmp, .png) to corresponding bits. 
input a small text "ST. Xaviers College". convert the text into bits.
now embed all bits of input text into image file(bit form). skip approximately 10000 bits 
and of the image and then start to embed bits of text file. 
finally convert all bits of image file to byte form.display new image file on screen. 
find if there any distortion.
